byline.original: By AZAM AHMED, PETER LATTMAN and BEN PROTESS

abstract: Rajat K. Gupta, the most prominent executive ensnared in an aggressive insider trading investigation and a former director of Goldman Sachs, is expected to surrender to the authorities.
